A few things to keep in mind:
1. The bank system is very very beta. You may lose stuff 2. Containers don't work. Don't even try to put a container in the vault 3. Stacks work just fine. 4. If the banker tells you that an item is unqiue, it's not properly in the bank database. Please report this on the boards (http://www.nordock.net) 5. Bank info, since it is saved on your character, is saved between crashes. 6. Bank gold is not counted in terms of death penalty for respawn. Use this to your advantage. 7. DO NOT MESS WITH THE TOKENS IN THE PERSISTENT TOOLBOXS IN YOUR INVENTORY! I can't stress that enough. The order that they are in is important. If you have more than one box, don't consolidate them to be helpful. Mess with them and you will lose stuff.
